{"tid":195302,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"戒煙日記 - DAY 3","createTime":"2017-04-10T13:43:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T04:23:55.000Z","uid":55017,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1181719d8bbfe50e6f38fd6c616e85adfeb78cc2","tid":195302,"uid":55017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:43:12.000Z","msg":"前幾晚番到屋企<br />\n食埋盒煙最後一支<br />\n突然好有衝動戒煙<br />\n可能因為前排老豆有Cancer<br />\n又有朋友屋企人Cancer死左<br />\n自己身體又弱<br />\n所以先諗到<br />\n<br />\n先補番day 1+2<br />\n<br />\nDay 1<br />\n早上起身冇咩feel<br />\n因為身上冇煙就算想食都食唔到<br />\n之後同女朋友出街<br />\n因為女朋友唔俾我食煙<br />\n我同佢出街時忍到<br />\n問題不大<br />\n但番屋企嗰陣好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見到七仔好想行入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後制止到自己"},{"pid":"3263636a28c47ea7f57fe20d38fbcd1659876afa","tid":195302,"uid":7514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:44:51.000Z","msg":"我第6日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戒到個人有躁狂症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有無貼戒煙貼？"},{"pid":"5d07f2eb73b040f750dc04be3bd57a4f43a0278c","tid":195302,"uid":7314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:45:57.000Z","msg":"&gt;戒煙第一部<br />\r\n&gt;唔買煙<br />\r\n&gt;食住電子煙頂住檔先<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt;頂<br />\r\n&gt;原來完全係兩回事<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt;吸落去果係水蒸氣咁<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt;無料到<br />\r\n&gt;頂下頂下<br />\r\n&gt;今日第四日冇買煙了<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt;尋日第三日果時<br />\r\n&gt;我覺得自己好似有d感冒<br />\r\n&gt;周身冇力<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt;訓醒又冇事<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt;而家又成日覺得個口好甜<br />\r\n&gt;真係要搵返d似煙味既煙油<br />\r\n&gt;"},{"pid":"0d40643027500ac101f9fe4333da49afa44a3a8a","tid":195302,"uid":55017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:47:29.000Z","msg":"Day 2<br />\n又係見女朋友既時間<br />\n所以忍到<br />\n但身體開始有啲變化<br />\n個胃唔舒服<br />\n長時間頂住頂住咁肚好脹<br />\n個人有啲燥㡳<br />\n送完女朋友番屋企即刻買左大量airwaves<br />\n準備長期作戰"},{"pid":"d1e0725243e8711ce9227b2d80b856055de0735d","tid":195302,"uid":100601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:51:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Day 2<br />\n又係見女朋友既時間<br />\n所以忍到<br />\n但身體開始有啲變化<br />\n個胃唔舒服<br />\n長時間頂住頂住咁肚好脹<br />\n個人有啲燥㡳<br />\n送完女朋友番屋企即刻買左大量airwaves<br />\n準備長期作戰</blockquote><br />\n食airwaves果隻糖，好正<br />\n食到上撚晒引，密過食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"910200e17dd8d721415b20c9de0d2882742d36fe","tid":195302,"uid":55017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:51:11.000Z","msg":"Day 3<br />\n個胃超唔舒服<br />\n有少少氣促同咳<br />\n食完個早餐個零鐘就肚餓搵嘢食<br />\n食左超過十粒香口膠<br />\n平時唔飲水今日飲到一支大既<br />\n同同事share我戒緊煙<br />\n佢叫我開post寫日記<br />\n大動力啲"},{"pid":"b0f95d5757bd7b863c0bbd705414b31bb3a9e2f7","tid":195302,"uid":55017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我第6日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n戒到個人有躁狂症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有無貼戒煙貼？</blockquote><br />\n冇<br />\n剩靠airwaves<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92f85699939d0967879bf0d2c1a3daa09646b58d","tid":195302,"uid":7314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:53:26.000Z","msg":"冇撚用的<br />\n好撚難戒<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 戒緊"},{"pid":"bee2eee90d6a90a90c1a50ae1318519d28cafdcf","tid":195302,"uid":55017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T13:53:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>&gt;戒煙第一部<br />\r\n&gt;唔買煙<br />\r\n&gt;食住電子煙頂住檔先<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt;頂<br />\r\n&gt;原來完全係兩回事<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt;吸落去果係水蒸氣咁<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt;無料到<br />\r\n&gt;頂下頂下<br />\r\n&gt;今日第四日冇買煙了<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt;尋日第三日果時<br />\r\n&gt;我覺得自己好似有d感冒<br />\r\n&gt;周身冇力<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt;訓醒又冇事<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt;<br />\r\n&gt;而家又成日覺得個口好甜<br />\r\n&gt;真係要搵返d似